com.io7m.jspatial.octtrees

Class OctTreeRaycastResult<T extends BoundingVolumeType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.io7m.jspatial.octtrees.OctTreeRaycastResult<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The precise type of octtree members.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<OctTreeRaycastResult<T>>

    public final class OctTreeRaycastResult<T extends BoundingVolumeType>
extends Object
implements Comparable<OctTreeRaycastResult<T>>

    An object returned by a successful raycast operation. Objects are ordered by their scalar distance from the origin of the ray.

    Note that although the OctTreeRaycastResult class is immutable, whether or not the object of type T returned by getObject() is mutable depends entirely on the user and therefore thread-safety is also the responsibility of the user.
